# 🚨 Alertify – Emergency Sound Detection App

**Alertify** is a production-grade accessibility app designed for the deaf and hard of hearing. It uses AI-powered real-time audio analysis to detect emergency sounds and alerts users with visual and haptic feedback.

---

## 📲 Download APK

[**⬇️ Download Alertify APK**](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1SWp1EAOuCMGCmPYrlsv6qFPjfYHwIIEq/view?usp=sharing)

> ⚠️ To install the APK, you may need to allow “Install from Unknown Sources” in your device settings.

