[Watch the Demo on YouTube](https://youtu.be/-Fh-dECzIoY?si=I7lbXXrlfI8lEsNK)  


---

## ⚙️ Features

- Detects 8 emergency sounds (alarms, sirens, glass break, etc.)
- Visual and haptic alerts
- Cloud sync with Supabase
- Works offline after install
- Accessibility-first design

---

## 🛠 Built With

- React Native + Expo SDK
- Supabase (for Auth & Data)
- Web Audio API
- TypeScript
- Expo AV

---

## 🔐 Privacy

- No audio is recorded or stored
- All detection is done in real-time, on-device
- Optional cloud sync with secure authentication

---

## 🧠 Inspiration

466 million people live with hearing loss. Many can't hear life-threatening sounds like fire alarms or sirens. Alertify gives them independence and safety — in real time.

